  <h2>Green by Default: Useful Work + Power-Optimized</h2>
  <p>
    Most "mining" burns energy to solve useless puzzles. Silica flips that:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Proof of Useful Work (PoUW):</strong> when the network needs extra security work, it channels compute into real tasks (think science/AI/analytics). Energy pulls double duty: securing the chain and doing something valuable.</li>
    <li><strong>Power-optimized:</strong> The network is tuned to avoid waste—smart scheduling, lightweight validation paths for home nodes, and sensible bandwidth caps so participation doesn't require a datacenter.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Result: a chain you can feel good about using.</p>

  <h2>Built for the Long Run: Post-Quantum Ready</h2>
  <p>
    Silica is designed with post-quantum-secure cryptography in mind. That means signatures and verification paths are selected (or upgrade-ready) to stand up to tomorrow's computing power—not just today's.
  </p>

  <div class="tech-details">
    <h3>Dual Key System for VRF Selection</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Long-term Identity Keys:</strong> Dilithium PQ signatures for accountability and governance</li>
      <li><strong>Ephemeral Epoch Keys:</strong> EC-VRF for unbiased validator selection, rotated every 5-10 minutes</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Multi-Factor Validator Weighting</h3>
    <pre><code>w_i = (1 + stake_i)^0.5 · (rep_i)^1.0 · (geo_i)^1.2</code></pre>
    <p>Where stake gets diminishing returns, reputation is linear, and geographic diversity gets a slight boost to prevent clustering.</p>
  </div>

  <p>This helps ensure fair, unpredictable validator selection that can't be gamed by stake concentration alone. It's peace of mind for long-term holders and builders.</p>

  <h2>Hands-off Rewards: "Savings by Default" PoS</h2>
  <p>No menus, no validator shopping, no anxiety.</p>

  <h3>Earn Automatically</h3>
  <p>Simply hold Chert in a compatible wallet or node and you earn rewards by default as part of Silica's Proof-of-Stake. Think of it like an on-chain savings account.</p>

  <div class="info-box">
    <h3>Example: Hold 1000 CHERT for 30 days</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Traditional Staking:</strong> Bond transaction → wait → unstake delay → claim rewards</li>
      <li><strong>Silica Auto-Staking:</strong> Balance earns 5-7% APY automatically, spend anytime with no delays</li>
      <li><strong>LockBox Option:</strong> Lock for 1 month → earn 1.15x multiplier, early exit with declining penalty</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p><strong>No slashing for regular holders:</strong> If you're just holding, you're safe. Operators who opt into running validators take on the operational risk; everyday holders don't.</p>
  <p><strong>Always liquid:</strong> Your coins stay in your wallet. Move them whenever you want—no complicated unbonding dance.</p>
  <p><strong>Optional boost:</strong> Want more? You can opt into simple "lockbox" terms for extra APY or run a tiny helper/Gateway process at home to earn a small bonus. Totally optional.</p>

